1
00:00:00,510 --> 00:00:01,910
(All people, incidents,
and backgrounds...)

2
00:00:01,910 --> 00:00:03,540
(in this drama are fictitious
and unrelated to reality.)

3
00:00:03,610 --> 00:00:05,340
(Also, children were filmed
under production guidelines.)

4
00:00:06,710 --> 00:00:08,110
(Episode 28)

5
00:00:15,120 --> 00:00:16,320
That's so true.

6
00:00:17,320 --> 00:00:18,920
- Yes.
- Right.

7
00:00:19,520 --> 00:00:22,330
My gosh, what is she doing here?

8
00:00:24,130 --> 00:00:25,400
Goodness, no way.

9
00:00:25,500 --> 00:00:27,500
- I know, the nerve of her to come.
- Exactly.

10
00:00:28,870 --> 00:00:30,170
Honestly, she has no shame.

11
00:00:30,770 --> 00:00:31,770
Seriously.

12
00:00:51,290 --> 00:00:53,360
- Oh my.
- My gosh!

13
00:00:53,560 --> 00:00:54,760
Goodness.

14
00:00:59,900 --> 00:01:00,900
What now?

15
00:01:01,500 --> 00:01:02,600
I can't believe this.

16
00:01:10,680 --> 00:01:12,410
Esteemed members of the
Women's Business Association.

17
00:01:14,050 --> 00:01:16,350
A mistress at
a prestigious gathering like this?

18
00:01:17,050 --> 00:01:19,850
I was so appalled
I had to come running.

19
00:01:20,020 --> 00:01:21,320
- I know.
- Seriously.

20
00:01:22,220 --> 00:01:24,490
This is embarrassing for all of us.

21
00:01:24,990 --> 00:01:27,290
This is unacceptable. How awful.

22
00:01:30,860 --> 00:01:33,570
Look at you, still trying to act
so high and mighty.

23
00:01:34,070 --> 00:01:36,200
The sight of you makes me sick.

24
00:01:40,610 --> 00:01:42,470
I'm sorry for causing a scene.

25
00:01:43,480 --> 00:01:45,510
I won't be staying today.

26
00:01:46,910 --> 00:01:48,080
See you next time.

27
00:01:49,880 --> 00:01:50,880
Next time?

28
00:01:51,850 --> 00:01:53,350
What makes you think
I won't show up next time?

29
00:01:53,990 --> 00:01:57,060
I'm going to follow you everywhere
and expose you.

30
00:01:59,090 --> 00:02:01,290
A company president?
A businesswoman?

31
00:02:01,930 --> 00:02:03,560
That's a laugh.

32
00:02:04,800 --> 00:02:07,400
You're just
the chairman's kept woman,

33
00:02:08,200 --> 00:02:09,370
and that's all you'll ever be.

34
00:02:19,980 --> 00:02:21,850
I've taken care of it
as you instructed.

35
00:02:23,950 --> 00:02:24,950
Good.

36
00:02:25,950 --> 00:02:27,820
She'll pay...

37
00:02:28,690 --> 00:02:32,260
for going behind my back
and crossing the line.

38
00:02:33,860 --> 00:02:37,500
Won't today's incident tarnish
the Adele Group's reputation?

39
00:02:40,060 --> 00:02:43,500
This is hardly the first time
Oh Jung Ran has made a scene.

40
00:02:44,700 --> 00:02:47,670
Everyone will gossip for a few days,
then it'll blow over.

41
00:02:49,470 --> 00:02:51,610
Besides, Kim Myung Hui needed
to be knocked down a peg...

42
00:02:52,340 --> 00:02:54,180
to learn her lesson.

43
00:02:54,750 --> 00:02:56,210
Yes, I understand.

44
00:02:58,280 --> 00:03:00,550
Now that Jung Ran is back,

45
00:03:02,350 --> 00:03:04,460
Myung Hui will realize
who she should...

46
00:03:04,890 --> 00:03:08,560
really be going up against
and what she should be focusing on.

47
00:03:09,830 --> 00:03:14,070
She won't have the luxury
of getting sidetracked by Temi Bio.

48
00:03:16,200 --> 00:03:19,940
Putting Myung Hui on the path
I've set for her...

49
00:03:20,570 --> 00:03:22,370
and ensuring Jung Ran
serves her purpose.

50
00:03:23,070 --> 00:03:25,080
Making sure all the pieces
are in place is,

51
00:03:25,540 --> 00:03:26,640
in the long run,

52
00:03:28,280 --> 00:03:30,110
also a way to protect...

53
00:03:31,580 --> 00:03:33,150
the Adele Group's reputation.

54
00:03:42,130 --> 00:03:45,000
It was your first invitation
to the Women's Business Association.

55
00:03:46,130 --> 00:03:49,330
A huge opportunity to win over
the board and shareholders,

56
00:03:49,330 --> 00:03:50,340
but Oh Jung Ran...

57
00:03:52,000 --> 00:03:54,110
How did she even know
you'd be there?

58
00:03:54,610 --> 00:03:57,510
She gets kicked out of the house,
so she tracks you down to lash out?

59
00:03:57,980 --> 00:03:59,740
It's so infuriating.

60
00:04:00,180 --> 00:04:01,510
I'm so mad.

61
00:04:01,510 --> 00:04:04,450
Was this really
her lashing out at me?

62
00:04:05,150 --> 00:04:06,180
What?

63
00:04:06,820 --> 00:04:10,220
I'm pretty sure this came
from Chairman Park's anger.

64
00:04:10,320 --> 00:04:11,390
Chairman Park?

65
00:04:12,090 --> 00:04:15,490
Because we were looking
into Temi Bio?

66
00:04:18,730 --> 00:04:22,230
Like Oh Jung Ran couldn't afford
to lose the bribery ledger,

67
00:04:22,930 --> 00:04:25,540
Chairman Park
couldn't just stand by...

68
00:04:25,800 --> 00:04:29,210
and let me keep digging
into Temi Bio.

69
00:04:29,740 --> 00:04:31,440
Then we're in big trouble.

70
00:04:31,940 --> 00:04:33,040
How will you survive...

71
00:04:33,040 --> 00:04:34,950
if Chairman Park
makes your life difficult?

72
00:04:35,410 --> 00:04:37,980
It could even weaken your position
in the succession race.

73
00:04:38,380 --> 00:04:39,380
We have to be smart.

74
00:04:39,380 --> 00:04:42,920
Let's stop investigating
Temi Bio ourselves.

75
00:04:43,520 --> 00:04:46,520
I'll look deeper into the art
from Eunhwa Trading...

76
00:04:46,620 --> 00:04:48,390
listed
in Oh Jung Ran's bribery ledger.

77
00:04:49,130 --> 00:04:50,160
Okay?

78
00:05:02,140 --> 00:05:04,010
So you're telling me
you called me back,

79
00:05:04,380 --> 00:05:07,410
not because of the ledger,
but because of Kim Myung Hui?

80
00:05:08,680 --> 00:05:11,720
Because it bothers you
that she's digging into Temi Bio?

81
00:05:13,220 --> 00:05:17,460
Keep a close eye on Myung Hui
and make sure she stays in line.

82
00:05:17,720 --> 00:05:18,860
If by any chance...

83
00:05:19,090 --> 00:05:22,790
she suspects that I was behind
the Temi Bio incident,

84
00:05:27,570 --> 00:05:29,900
make her believe you did it.

85
00:05:30,000 --> 00:05:31,640
That's what you're here for.

86
00:05:33,500 --> 00:05:35,840
Am I just your puppet and scapegoat?

87
00:05:36,970 --> 00:05:39,680
A scapegoat to hide
your cruelty from her,

88
00:05:39,680 --> 00:05:41,780
a shield to deflect her suspicions?

89
00:05:42,780 --> 00:05:45,750
If you don't like it,
don't come home.

90
00:05:47,250 --> 00:05:48,820
What am I to you?

91
00:05:49,990 --> 00:05:54,030
I've been Hyun Jun's mother and
your wife for over 30 years.

92
00:05:55,060 --> 00:05:56,460
How could you...

93
00:05:57,400 --> 00:05:58,800
use me like this?

94
00:06:00,230 --> 00:06:03,070
Don't you care
if you drag my heart through the mud?

95
00:06:03,870 --> 00:06:06,000
Is that tramp all you care about?

96
00:06:06,000 --> 00:06:07,840
Kim Myung Hui...

97
00:06:10,440 --> 00:06:13,040
survived your attempt on her life...

98
00:06:13,280 --> 00:06:15,980
and managed to protect my son.

99
00:06:16,050 --> 00:06:17,380
That's not the only reason
you got to live...

100
00:06:17,380 --> 00:06:18,680
as the lady of the Adele Group,

101
00:06:18,820 --> 00:06:21,020
and not as a murderer!

102
00:06:23,820 --> 00:06:25,820
(Chairman Park Tae Ho)

103
00:06:27,530 --> 00:06:31,860
I'm only letting you back
because I need you to keep her in line,

104
00:06:32,730 --> 00:06:34,870
so stop picking fights
for no reason.

105
00:06:35,870 --> 00:06:37,400
As for your feelings,

106
00:06:38,440 --> 00:06:39,840
deal with them yourself.

107
00:06:41,710 --> 00:06:43,240
All thanks to her?

108
00:06:45,380 --> 00:06:47,350
Park Tae Ho, you truly are...

109
00:06:48,710 --> 00:06:50,250
cruel and heartless.

110
00:07:04,900 --> 00:07:06,730
What should I do
about Ms. Oh's ledger?

111
00:07:07,570 --> 00:07:08,570
Leave it.

112
00:07:08,670 --> 00:07:11,600
All it does
is expose her dirty secrets.

113
00:07:19,480 --> 00:07:22,710
(Adele Group's Rapid Expansion)

114
00:07:25,750 --> 00:07:26,780
Jung Ran?

115
00:07:27,920 --> 00:07:28,920
Are you crying?

116
00:07:29,990 --> 00:07:31,060
Shut it.

117
00:07:31,560 --> 00:07:35,760
Weren't you thrilled
that Tae Ho allowed you back home?

118
00:07:35,990 --> 00:07:37,700
What's wrong?

119
00:07:38,530 --> 00:07:40,670
I'll claim my place
as the lady of Adele...

120
00:07:41,270 --> 00:07:42,630
and show them all...

121
00:07:43,400 --> 00:07:45,240
what I'm made of.

122
00:07:49,140 --> 00:07:50,170
Jung Ran, wait.

123
00:07:51,940 --> 00:07:52,940
My gosh.

124
00:07:58,120 --> 00:08:00,650
Chairman Park allowed her back home?

125
00:08:01,950 --> 00:08:03,390
How did Oh Jung Ran...

126
00:08:03,920 --> 00:08:06,090
get Chairman Park
to change his mind?

127
00:08:06,660 --> 00:08:11,130
Did she press on his weaknesses
or use some leverage against him?

128
00:08:14,930 --> 00:08:17,070
You want to see my mother?

129
00:08:18,970 --> 00:08:20,810
I overheard
near the chairman's office...

130
00:08:20,810 --> 00:08:22,810
that she's finally moving back home.

131
00:08:23,670 --> 00:08:25,940
Really?
I didn't think it'd be this soon.

132
00:08:29,780 --> 00:08:32,250
She went as far
as kidnapping someone...

133
00:08:32,820 --> 00:08:34,650
and putting you through all that.

134
00:08:35,490 --> 00:08:37,320
I'm sorry
she wasn't punished longer.

135
00:08:38,260 --> 00:08:39,820
There's no need to apologize.

136
00:08:39,920 --> 00:08:42,490
As far as I'm concerned, it's over.

137
00:08:44,400 --> 00:08:48,200
That's why I need to tie up
my own loose ends.

138
00:08:50,070 --> 00:08:51,670
Your mother's phone.

139
00:08:52,600 --> 00:08:54,140
Right, the phone...

140
00:08:54,540 --> 00:08:56,470
Yes, I remember.

141
00:08:59,710 --> 00:09:02,310
If it's just about the phone,
you can give it to me.

142
00:09:02,750 --> 00:09:04,620
Things weren't pretty last time,

143
00:09:04,620 --> 00:09:07,390
so you don't have to see her
in person.

144
00:09:07,790 --> 00:09:10,690
That's precisely
why I need to see her.

145
00:09:11,120 --> 00:09:13,390
I don't want there to be
any hard feelings.

146
00:09:14,360 --> 00:09:18,330
I'll return her phone, apologize,
and try to make amends.

147
00:09:20,500 --> 00:09:22,300
When you put it like that,

148
00:09:22,600 --> 00:09:24,140
it's hard not to fall for you
all over again.

149
00:09:25,440 --> 00:09:28,840
We'll go together after work.
I'll get everything ready.

150
00:09:39,050 --> 00:09:40,220
What's that?

151
00:09:40,380 --> 00:09:42,250
(Bion Tech)

152
00:09:42,390 --> 00:09:44,090
Well, it's...

153
00:09:46,790 --> 00:09:48,330
I felt bad.

154
00:09:49,890 --> 00:09:51,700
What do you feel so bad about?

155
00:09:53,630 --> 00:09:55,170
The false accusation?

156
00:09:56,100 --> 00:09:59,270
Or for grilling me
with those strange questions?

157
00:09:59,740 --> 00:10:03,210
The fact that despite all that,
I'm still waiting for your answer.

158
00:10:07,610 --> 00:10:10,480
I'm sorry for asking
such strange and awkward questions,

159
00:10:10,780 --> 00:10:13,580
but I know what I heard,
and I need an answer from you.

160
00:10:13,920 --> 00:10:16,690
It's not wishful thinking
or a distorted memory.

161
00:10:17,860 --> 00:10:19,190
So I can't back down.

162
00:10:22,690 --> 00:10:24,530
You still only see me...

163
00:10:26,630 --> 00:10:28,330
as that dead woman.

164
00:10:37,270 --> 00:10:40,180
I can't accept feelings like this
from you.

165
00:10:41,210 --> 00:10:44,320
You need to figure out
where your heart...

166
00:10:45,350 --> 00:10:46,750
truly belongs.

167
00:11:15,150 --> 00:11:16,380
Mrs. Ok.

168
00:11:17,180 --> 00:11:18,480
Mrs. Ok!

169
00:11:21,520 --> 00:11:22,520
You're home, ma'am.

170
00:11:24,320 --> 00:11:26,190
You heard I was coming, didn't you?

171
00:11:26,660 --> 00:11:28,860
Yes, Manager Kang told me.

172
00:11:28,860 --> 00:11:29,860
Then,

173
00:11:30,930 --> 00:11:32,160
come stand in front of me.

174
00:11:33,100 --> 00:11:34,100
Ma'am?

175
00:11:34,400 --> 00:11:37,330
Stand in front of me.
Was I not clear?

176
00:11:56,050 --> 00:11:57,220
Why aren't you moving?

177
00:11:57,890 --> 00:11:59,490
I told you to get over here!

178
00:11:59,820 --> 00:12:02,460
Jung Ran, what's gotten into you?

179
00:12:03,260 --> 00:12:04,700
Zip it and stay out of this.

180
00:12:15,110 --> 00:12:16,110
Kneel.

181
00:12:16,770 --> 00:12:17,780
Sorry?

182
00:12:20,740 --> 00:12:22,810
How dare a mere housekeeper...

183
00:12:23,350 --> 00:12:26,420
not even greet the lady of the house
properly at the door...

184
00:12:26,480 --> 00:12:27,620
after hearing she was returning?

185
00:12:29,120 --> 00:12:30,820
You didn't even bow.

186
00:12:32,160 --> 00:12:33,820
The nerve.

187
00:12:35,290 --> 00:12:37,090
Either pack your bags
and get out right now,

188
00:12:37,560 --> 00:12:39,660
or get on your knees
and beg for my forgiveness.

189
00:12:41,600 --> 00:12:42,600
That's enough.

190
00:12:42,930 --> 00:12:45,100
Don't take your anger out
on an innocent person.

191
00:12:46,400 --> 00:12:48,540
- Ma'am!
- Jung Ran!

192
00:12:52,240 --> 00:12:53,240
Of course.

193
00:12:54,040 --> 00:12:57,280
The housekeeper only disrespects me
because the mistress is arrogant.

194
00:12:58,250 --> 00:12:59,920
Before you talk
about proper behavior,

195
00:13:00,180 --> 00:13:02,120
learn how to act first.

196
00:13:03,250 --> 00:13:06,090
Bow your head and respond...

197
00:13:07,120 --> 00:13:08,630
with "Yes, ma'am."

198
00:13:19,100 --> 00:13:23,040
It's all my fault.
I ask for your forgiveness, ma'am.

199
00:13:23,110 --> 00:13:27,210
There you go, Jung Ran.
I'm sure they all got the message.

200
00:13:27,210 --> 00:13:28,210
All of you!

201
00:13:29,950 --> 00:13:31,750
From now on, you'd better behave.

202
00:13:32,820 --> 00:13:36,320
Don't you dare defy me.
Answer with "Yes, ma'am,"

203
00:13:37,290 --> 00:13:38,860
and show respect.

204
00:13:39,620 --> 00:13:40,620
Got it?

205
00:13:41,290 --> 00:13:42,490
Yes, ma'am.

206
00:13:56,740 --> 00:13:58,440
You still won't say it?

207
00:13:59,410 --> 00:14:00,410
Fine.

208
00:14:01,010 --> 00:14:02,550
Go on, keep it up.

209
00:14:03,210 --> 00:14:06,220
I'll keep slapping Butler Ok
until her cheek is raw.

210
00:14:06,550 --> 00:14:07,550
Stop.

211
00:14:13,490 --> 00:14:15,130
Please stop, ma'am.

212
00:14:26,740 --> 00:14:29,640
No matter what you do,
Park Tae Ho can't get rid of me.

213
00:14:31,210 --> 00:14:34,140
Until the day I die,
I'm the Adele Group chairman's wife,

214
00:14:35,110 --> 00:14:36,550
and the heir to Adele...

215
00:14:37,150 --> 00:14:39,150
will be my son, never yours.

216
00:14:55,630 --> 00:14:56,800
Are you all right?

217
00:14:57,900 --> 00:15:00,040
I'm all right.

218
00:15:00,470 --> 00:15:02,840
What about you, ma'am?
Are you all right?

219
00:15:03,640 --> 00:15:05,240
Yes, I'm fine.

220
00:15:27,830 --> 00:15:31,640
What happened
in the chairman's office earlier?

221
00:15:33,240 --> 00:15:36,070
What did that jerk Park Tae Ho say
to make you leave in tears...

222
00:15:36,410 --> 00:15:38,510
and start cracking down
on the staff?

223
00:15:39,280 --> 00:15:40,780
Stop bothering me and leave.

224
00:16:06,840 --> 00:16:08,010
What's going on with you two?

225
00:16:08,740 --> 00:16:10,140
What happened to your faces?

226
00:16:15,450 --> 00:16:16,450
Mrs. Ok.

227
00:16:19,020 --> 00:16:20,320
Ms. Oh said...

228
00:16:20,720 --> 00:16:22,820
we were acting out of line.

229
00:16:23,450 --> 00:16:25,760
So she slapped you?

230
00:16:34,800 --> 00:16:36,500
Darn. Come here.

231
00:16:39,300 --> 00:16:40,300
Wait.

232
00:16:46,740 --> 00:16:47,750
What?

233
00:16:49,750 --> 00:16:51,010
It's nothing.

234
00:16:54,650 --> 00:16:56,550
It's just that Jung Ran seems
to be in pain.

235
00:16:57,450 --> 00:16:59,960
Could you please check on her?

236
00:17:00,560 --> 00:17:03,630
She couldn't control her temper
and slapped people,

237
00:17:03,630 --> 00:17:05,330
and now she's sick? As if.

238
00:17:05,330 --> 00:17:06,330
But still...

239
00:17:06,630 --> 00:17:09,030
If she's that sick,
tell her to see a doctor.

240
00:17:09,970 --> 00:17:12,270
I have to head back out
for a dinner meeting.

241
00:17:41,730 --> 00:17:43,970
Honestly, that Oh Jung Ran.

242
00:17:45,100 --> 00:17:48,710
I didn't mean for Myung Hui
to get hurt like this.

243
00:17:50,240 --> 00:17:51,940
You must resent me...

244
00:17:53,040 --> 00:17:55,150
for bringing my wife back...

245
00:17:56,880 --> 00:17:58,920
and putting you
through this humiliation.

246
00:18:02,120 --> 00:18:04,190
It hurt less than having wine
thrown in my face...

247
00:18:04,960 --> 00:18:07,760
at the Women's Business Association
meeting.

248
00:18:09,130 --> 00:18:10,360
It was you, wasn't it?

249
00:18:11,230 --> 00:18:12,400
You're the one...

250
00:18:13,230 --> 00:18:15,230
who sent your wife to that event.

251
00:18:19,440 --> 00:18:22,870
What did I do that was so wrong...

252
00:18:24,110 --> 00:18:26,610
to upset you like this?

253
00:18:36,490 --> 00:18:37,720
I was simply thinking...

254
00:18:39,020 --> 00:18:41,660
about keeping things balanced
in this family.

255
00:18:42,830 --> 00:18:45,960
Until a successor to the Adele Group
is chosen,

256
00:18:47,530 --> 00:18:51,030
both my wife and you need...

257
00:18:52,740 --> 00:18:54,910
to stay in your place.

258
00:18:58,980 --> 00:19:00,080
I see.

259
00:19:02,480 --> 00:19:03,710
I understand.

260
00:19:16,060 --> 00:19:17,060
Liar.

261
00:19:18,500 --> 00:19:19,960
You, Park Tae Ho,

262
00:19:20,400 --> 00:19:22,730
are just trying to stop me
any way you can.

263
00:19:23,200 --> 00:19:26,070
My digging into Temi Bio
behind your back...

264
00:19:26,770 --> 00:19:30,210
must have made you retaliate
by humiliating me like this.

265
00:19:35,110 --> 00:19:36,380
How will you survive...

266
00:19:36,380 --> 00:19:38,250
if Chairman Park
makes your life difficult?

267
00:19:38,780 --> 00:19:41,220
It could even weaken your position
in the succession race.

268
00:19:42,820 --> 00:19:43,820
We have to be smart.

269
00:19:44,450 --> 00:19:48,160
Let's stop investigating
Temi Bio ourselves.

270
00:19:49,390 --> 00:19:50,390
No,

271
00:19:51,230 --> 00:19:55,400
I need to find out
why Temi Bio bothers him so much.

272
00:19:57,070 --> 00:19:59,370
If I let this humiliation
scare me off,

273
00:20:00,070 --> 00:20:01,540
I'll never be able to defeat...

274
00:20:02,410 --> 00:20:03,970
Oh Jung Ran and Park Tae Ho.

275
00:20:16,150 --> 00:20:17,850
Is this really how it ends,

276
00:20:19,390 --> 00:20:21,120
with nothing to my name,

277
00:20:21,490 --> 00:20:23,230
just getting kicked out like this?

278
00:20:35,370 --> 00:20:37,470
I'm not the one
who deserves the blame.

279
00:20:40,110 --> 00:20:41,750
It's Chairman Park Tae Ho!

280
00:20:45,520 --> 00:20:46,550
No.

281
00:20:47,280 --> 00:20:48,950
Why did I get my hands dirty
in the first place?

282
00:20:50,220 --> 00:20:53,920
I won't let anyone take the future I built
with my own two hands.

283
00:20:57,260 --> 00:20:58,530
I have to find a way...

284
00:20:59,260 --> 00:21:02,300
to protect my future
from Chairman Park.

285
00:21:14,040 --> 00:21:16,850
Our doorstep is going to wear out...

286
00:21:16,850 --> 00:21:18,680
with all these fancy people
from Adele...

287
00:21:18,750 --> 00:21:20,120
coming and going all the time.

288
00:21:21,350 --> 00:21:22,490
Keep it down.

289
00:21:22,590 --> 00:21:25,660
We need to make a good impression
so Yu Na can get her job back.

290
00:21:28,160 --> 00:21:31,330
What brings you all the way out here
at this hour?

291
00:21:32,630 --> 00:21:34,830
Is Ms. Choi home?

292
00:21:52,950 --> 00:21:55,020
What are you here
to dig up this time?

293
00:21:56,220 --> 00:22:00,620
Search all you want.
I'm not hiding anything.

294
00:22:02,030 --> 00:22:03,390
Maybe not evidence,

295
00:22:03,990 --> 00:22:05,760
but it does look like
you have a secret.

296
00:22:07,030 --> 00:22:08,400
What secret?

297
00:22:08,900 --> 00:22:10,070
Temi Bio.

298
00:22:13,440 --> 00:22:15,540
I saw you and Ms. Oh...

299
00:22:16,740 --> 00:22:20,680
pleading desperately
with the chairman.

300
00:22:22,780 --> 00:22:24,080
Why did you...

301
00:22:24,510 --> 00:22:26,850
play the Temi Bio card to get...

302
00:22:27,680 --> 00:22:29,190
your termination reversed?

303
00:22:31,350 --> 00:22:33,390
You, the chairman,

304
00:22:35,730 --> 00:22:37,130
and Temi Bio.

305
00:22:37,830 --> 00:22:39,260
There's something between you,
isn't there?

306
00:22:44,770 --> 00:22:47,700
Does the chairman know
that you're...

307
00:22:48,710 --> 00:22:51,110
going around digging into Temi Bio?

308
00:22:52,240 --> 00:22:54,880
Is that something
the chairman shouldn't know about?

309
00:22:55,750 --> 00:22:59,280
I was right. There's a secret.

310
00:23:02,520 --> 00:23:04,760
What secret?

311
00:23:05,220 --> 00:23:08,490
I only asked because you're acting
like there's some big secret...

312
00:23:08,890 --> 00:23:10,160
when there isn't.

313
00:23:12,860 --> 00:23:13,930
Fair enough.

314
00:23:15,570 --> 00:23:18,870
I did consider
that there might be nothing to it.

315
00:23:19,640 --> 00:23:22,910
Ms. Oh got back in
by leveraging her bribery ledger,

316
00:23:24,140 --> 00:23:28,680
but your Temi Bio card
doesn't seem to have worked.

317
00:23:30,380 --> 00:23:33,420
Ms. Oh is back home?
The chairman let her in?

318
00:23:34,350 --> 00:23:37,150
Apparently,
the bribery ledger worked.

319
00:23:39,560 --> 00:23:43,360
I was just checking to see
if you'd be back at the office.

320
00:23:44,290 --> 00:23:47,830
But since this is a dead end,
I'll be on my way.

321
00:24:02,480 --> 00:24:04,710
If they really share a secret,

322
00:24:04,980 --> 00:24:07,620
she'll play the Temi Bio card again.

323
00:24:21,870 --> 00:24:23,830
Here. It's Ms. Oh's phone.

324
00:24:25,800 --> 00:24:27,200
Do you really have to go there
in person?

325
00:24:28,410 --> 00:24:30,540
Knowing her personality,
she'll likely give you a hard time.

326
00:24:30,640 --> 00:24:32,940
It's a risk I have to take
to get information.

327
00:24:34,080 --> 00:24:36,250
If I can get on her good side
with this,

328
00:24:37,310 --> 00:24:39,280
it'll help our plan.

329
00:24:40,050 --> 00:24:41,080
Chloe.

330
00:24:45,120 --> 00:24:46,620
Father, I didn't see you there.

331
00:24:47,390 --> 00:24:48,860
I was just dropping off the phone.

332
00:24:49,690 --> 00:24:51,160
I hear she's on her way
to see your mother.

333
00:24:51,700 --> 00:24:52,860
Please take good care of my Chloe.

334
00:24:53,360 --> 00:24:54,360
Right, of course.

335
00:24:56,030 --> 00:24:58,030
The way you're asking,

336
00:24:59,240 --> 00:25:01,470
it feels like we're a couple
going to meet my parents.

337
00:25:02,840 --> 00:25:03,840
Excuse me?

338
00:25:04,610 --> 00:25:06,840
Oh, it's nothing.

339
00:25:07,110 --> 00:25:08,980
I'll make sure she's safe.
Don't worry.

340
00:25:10,510 --> 00:25:12,150
Since she's going to apologize
in person,

341
00:25:13,420 --> 00:25:14,850
I'm sure my mom will come around.

342
00:25:17,150 --> 00:25:18,150
Let's get going.

343
00:25:18,890 --> 00:25:19,890
We'll be on our way then.

344
00:25:33,600 --> 00:25:34,870
Hyun Jun!

345
00:25:35,470 --> 00:25:38,110
You have no idea
how good it is to see you.

346
00:25:39,540 --> 00:25:41,410
We're back home.

347
00:25:42,950 --> 00:25:47,120
Wait. What's Chloe,
or whatever her name is, doing here?

348
00:25:47,780 --> 00:25:50,690
Mr. Song, it's just Chloe.

349
00:25:51,220 --> 00:25:54,090
Sorry.
It's just what your mom calls her.

350
00:25:54,520 --> 00:25:55,590
Where's Ms. Oh?

351
00:25:56,060 --> 00:26:00,100
In her room.
But she's in a bit of a mood.

352
00:26:00,500 --> 00:26:01,500
Ms. Oh.

353
00:26:02,670 --> 00:26:03,670
Ms. Oh!

354
00:26:16,610 --> 00:26:18,420
You acted like you were never going
to see me again.

355
00:26:19,920 --> 00:26:21,180
Are you even glad I'm back?

356
00:26:23,790 --> 00:26:24,790
That's not it.

357
00:26:25,490 --> 00:26:26,520
Someone's here to see you.

358
00:26:29,960 --> 00:26:32,130
It's Chloe. You remember her, right?

359
00:26:36,800 --> 00:26:38,070
You little thief.

360
00:26:38,840 --> 00:26:41,200
- How dare you show your face here?
- Mom.

361
00:26:41,270 --> 00:26:42,640
I'm very sorry.

362
00:26:43,010 --> 00:26:46,540
I was desperate at the time,
and I went about it the wrong way.

363
00:26:46,880 --> 00:26:51,180
Now that the case is closed,
I was hoping we could move on.

364
00:26:52,080 --> 00:26:55,320
I brought the clothes you mentioned
and your cell phone.

365
00:27:01,460 --> 00:27:03,390
Come on, Jung Ran.

366
00:27:03,890 --> 00:27:07,760
She even brought you gifts.
You could at least accept them.

367
00:27:08,230 --> 00:27:11,740
Like Chloe said,
it'd be good for us all to move on.

368
00:27:13,170 --> 00:27:14,370
As if.

369
00:27:15,610 --> 00:27:17,770
Now even this little thief
is disrespecting me.

370
00:27:18,480 --> 00:27:21,410
Did you think I could be bought off
with a cheap outfit?

371
00:27:22,710 --> 00:27:25,550
You think you can walk all over
the lady of Adele?

372
00:27:29,350 --> 00:27:32,290
- Ms. Oh, that's enough.
- You, wake up.

373
00:27:33,390 --> 00:27:36,960
This thing is just using you
to get to me.

374
00:27:40,830 --> 00:27:41,900
What's your game?

375
00:27:42,200 --> 00:27:44,600
What are you trying
to get out of me?

376
00:27:45,270 --> 00:27:47,670
What are you up to,
using my son like this?

377
00:27:47,670 --> 00:27:48,840
Mom!

378
00:27:56,380 --> 00:27:57,380
Hey!

379
00:27:58,880 --> 00:28:00,020
Where do you think you're going?

380
00:28:00,380 --> 00:28:01,380
See?

381
00:28:01,380 --> 00:28:04,720
That Chloe, or whatever her name is,
is working with Kim Myung Hui.

382
00:28:04,720 --> 00:28:07,320
That's why Min Jun
keeps coming to her aid.

383
00:28:07,390 --> 00:28:09,030
Like you know anything!

384
00:28:10,890 --> 00:28:12,100
Don't talk about her like that.

385
00:28:14,100 --> 00:28:15,100
Chloe!

386
00:28:32,950 --> 00:28:34,180
What do you think you're doing?

387
00:28:34,180 --> 00:28:36,150
That's what I should be asking you.

388
00:28:37,450 --> 00:28:39,760
Why would someone like you
just stand there and take that?

389
00:28:39,790 --> 00:28:42,130
I can take care of myself.

390
00:28:42,690 --> 00:28:44,560
Whatever I do, just stay out of it.

391
00:28:44,560 --> 00:28:46,230
I'm not the woman who died.

392
00:28:52,040 --> 00:28:53,040
Park Min Jun!

393
00:28:54,640 --> 00:28:55,710
What do you think you're doing?

394
00:28:56,910 --> 00:28:58,710
What good is storming out
going to do here?

395
00:28:58,880 --> 00:29:00,340
Was I supposed to just stand by...

396
00:29:00,340 --> 00:29:01,610
while she was being treated
like that?

397
00:29:01,710 --> 00:29:03,450
Who are you to butt in?

398
00:29:03,450 --> 00:29:05,820
You weren't doing anything about it!

399
00:29:07,520 --> 00:29:09,890
While your mother was spewing
all that venom,

400
00:29:10,520 --> 00:29:11,920
you didn't do anything.

401
00:29:13,920 --> 00:29:17,390
And I know just how much that hurts.

402
00:29:22,300 --> 00:29:23,370
That's enough, both of you.

403
00:29:24,330 --> 00:29:25,440
I'm leaving now.

404
00:29:28,840 --> 00:29:31,070
I'll go with you.
Let me take you home.

405
00:29:36,510 --> 00:29:37,650
She's here as my guest.

406
00:29:38,520 --> 00:29:39,520
Actually,

407
00:29:44,890 --> 00:29:46,260
she's the woman I like.

408
00:29:53,060 --> 00:29:54,530
Right now, Chloe and I...

409
00:30:00,040 --> 00:30:02,210
could use some time alone.

410
00:30:05,840 --> 00:30:06,880
So let go of her hand...

411
00:30:08,850 --> 00:30:09,850
and back off.

412
00:30:40,440 --> 00:30:41,440
No.

413
00:30:42,480 --> 00:30:43,750
I don't want to let her go.

414
00:30:45,250 --> 00:30:47,320
No matter what anyone says or why,

415
00:30:49,290 --> 00:30:50,390
I don't want to let her go.

416
00:31:33,930 --> 00:31:36,970
(Pearl in Red)

417
00:31:37,030 --> 00:31:39,140
Just like you're being true
to your feelings,

418
00:31:39,140 --> 00:31:40,840
I'm going to follow my heart.

419
00:31:40,840 --> 00:31:42,010
What if those feelings...

420
00:31:42,010 --> 00:31:43,170
- aren't real?
- Not real?

421
00:31:43,170 --> 00:31:46,240
All you two seem to care about
is your own feelings.

422
00:31:46,340 --> 00:31:48,780
Don't you think you're being
incredibly one-sided and rude?

423
00:31:48,850 --> 00:31:51,480
- Now I can get it all back.
- Choi Yu Na, you...

424
00:31:51,550 --> 00:31:53,750
My future and Park Min Jun.

425
00:31:54,320 --> 00:31:56,950
Is Ms. Choi really coming back?

426
00:31:57,020 --> 00:31:59,190
- Looks like it.
- Good morning.

427
00:31:59,460 --> 00:32:00,890
It's good to see you again.

428
00:32:02,260 --> 00:32:04,260
(Subtitles are provided by KOCOWA.)
